These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, indie, disco, soul
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, cola
1. the person drinking water is the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the fan of indie##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
5. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person drinking cola is between the fan of soul and the person who's hobby is hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | writing      | hiking | reading | skydiving |
| Music-Genre   | disco | classical  | indie   | soul    |
| Beverage     | water     | almond-milk    | cola    | hot-chocolate      |

