.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, adventure, western, animation
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, dahlia, rose, balloon-flower
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
2. the person watching animation movies is the person who growsrose##1
3. the person watching western movies is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
7. the person who growsmarigold is between the person watching animation movies and the person watching adventure movies##2
8. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person who growsdahlia and the person watching western movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre         | animation | western   | adventure | mystery  |
| Flower   | rose     | marigold | balloon-flower  | dahlia |
| Transport     | taxi        | jet-ski  | boat    | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, march, september, august
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, canadian, german
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, filmmaking, collecting, rock-climbing
1. the german is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in august##2
2. the argentine is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4
6. the canadian is between the person who's birthday is in march and the american##2
7. the german is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Birthday          | july | march   | august     | september     |
| Nationality   | argentine  | german | canadian   | american  |
| Hobby     | rock-climbing      | filmmaking | collecting | drawing |

