.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, horror, romance
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, blood-red, turquise, orange
City: miami, venice, marseilles, prague
1. the person who likes orange is in an even position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person traveling to venice##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
4. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
5. the person who likes orange is the person traveling to miami##1
6. the person watching horror movies is the person who likes fuchsia##1
7. the person who likes turquise is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | romance   | horror     | disaster |
| Color   | turquise  | orange      | fuchsia        | blood-red     |
| City         | marseilles | miami | prague | venice   |

