.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, iced-tea, coffee, mirinda
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, orchid, daisy, begonia
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, jet-ski, van
1. the person drinking mirinda is the person who growsbegonia##1
2. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the bus is the person who growsbegonia##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
6. the person who growsorchid is on the far left##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
8. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
9. the person who growsmarigold is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage   | tea   | mirinda   | coffee | iced-tea |
| Flower         | orchid      | begonia | marigold      | daisy |
| Transport     | helicopter | bus        | van       | jet-ski  |

