.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, amaryllis, sunflower, zinnia
House: cape-cod, tower, ranch-style, townhouse
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, hamster, rat
1. the person who growsamaryllis is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the tower house is on the far right##1
6. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
7. the person who growszinnia is in an even position##4
8. the townhouse house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Flower    | sunflower   | zinnia      | amaryllis       | azalea |
| House   | cape-cod | townhouse | ranch-style     | tower |
| Pet     | rat     | guinea-pig  | chinchilla | hamster |

