.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, lemonade, tea
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, monopoly, go, poker
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, aconite, rose, sunflower
1. the person who growsrose is the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person who growsaconite is between the person playing poker and the person who growszinnia##2
3. the person playing poker is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
6. the person playing poker is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
7. the person playing mah-jongg is the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person who growsrose is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | tea          | hot-chocolate | 7up        |
| Game   | go     | monopoly | poker   | mah-jongg     |
| Flower           | zinnia | aconite         | sunflower         | rose |

