.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, collecting, drawing, singing
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, tram, skateboard, train
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, ferret, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
2. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person driving the train is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person driving the car and the person who's hobby is chess##2
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
7. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting | chess      | drawing       | singing    |
| Transport           | tram  | skateboard  | train | car |
| Pet   | rabbit      | ferret | guinea-pig         | chinchilla    |

