.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
House: gothic-revival, cape-cod, victorian, craftsman
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, fonseca, bluemaster, bolivar
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, skiing, weightlifting
1. the oliveros-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
3. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
5. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
7. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
8. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the victorian house##1
9. the bolivar-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| House   | cape-cod         | gothic-revival  | victorian     | craftsman         |
| Cigar        | bolivar | fonseca | oliveros | bluemaster         |
| Sport      | rugby         | skiing  | ice-hockey   | weightlifting |

