.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, lilac, azure, lavender
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, malaysian, nigerian, turkish
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, skateboard, helicopter, bike
 1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3
 2. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 4. the nigerian is between the person who likes lilac and the person who likes ivory##2
 5. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
 6. the person driving the bike is the person who likes azure##1
 7. the turkish is on the far right##1
 8. the person who likes ivory is in an odd position##4
 9. the malaysian is between the person who likes lavender and the person who likes azure##2
10. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Color   | ivory  | azure    | lilac | lavender    |
| Nationality   | canadian | nigerian | malaysian  | turkish |
| Transport           | helicopter   | bike    | trike        | skateboard   |

