.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, may, june, july
City: liverpool, marseilles, hamburg, rome
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, indonesian, italian, russian
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the russian is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
4. the person traveling to marseilles is in an even position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
6. the russian is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
7. the indonesian is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
9. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Birthday      | february                | july  | may | june   |
| City           | rome | marseilles | liverpool   | hamburg |
| Nationality   | indonesian         | dutch     | russian     | italian |

