.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, dutch, nigerian, russian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, musical, romance, western
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, hiking, sudoku, fishing
1. the dutch is on the left of the russian##1
2. the nigerian is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
4. the nigerian is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person watching western movies and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
6. the person watching romance movies is in an even position##4
7. the brazilian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Nationality          | nigerian    | dutch  | russian  | brazilian |
| Movie-Genre   | western | musical | action | romance |
| Hobby   | sudoku    | magic-tricks     | fishing    | hiking |

