.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
4 different games are played: bridge, canasta, domino, whist
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, fishing, sudoku, reading
4 different pets are kept: goat, horse, pony, turtle
1. the owner of the horse is between the person playing domino and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
2. the person playing bridge is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
4. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
5. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
6. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person playing bridge##1
9. the person who's hobby is reading is between the owner of the pony and the owner of the goat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Game      | bridge | domino      | canasta  | whist    |
| Hobby   | sudoku   | fishing | reading | collecting |
| Pet           | turtle      | pony       | horse   | goat      |

