.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, february, october, april
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, project-manager, bartender, designer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, golf, handball, lacrosse
1. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's sport is cycling##2
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the designer is between the person who's sport is cycling and the chef##2
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
8. the project-manager is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday         | august    | october | february  | april  |
| Job   | bartender | project-manager       | designer | chef |
| Sport         | handball   | cycling      | lacrosse | golf       |

