4. the bartender is the person traveling to rome##1
5. the bartender is on the far left##1
6. the person traveling to prague is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the dancer##1
8. the owner of the lizard is the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Job      | bartender      | freelancer | manager     | dancer    |
| City   | rome | prague      | hamburg | san-francisco |
| Pet           | hamster   | guinea-pig  | cat     | lizard |

